<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy" %>
<% meta_description "#{forum_name} Privacy Policy — how we collect, use, and protect your information." %>
<% canonical_url privacy_url %>
<% noindex_page %>

<div style="max-width:740px; margin:0 auto;">
  <div style="background:#242424; border:1px solid #444;">
    <div style="background:#303030; border-bottom:1px solid #444; padding:8px 14px; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold; color:#e0e0e0;">
      Privacy Policy
    </div>
    <div style="padding:16px 20px; font-size:12px; line-height:1.8; color:#b0b0b0;">

      <p style="color:#888; font-size:11px; margin-bottom:14px;">Last updated: <%= Date.today.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">1. Information We Collect</h3>
      <p>When you register, we collect your username and optionally your email address. When you use the Forum, we collect:</p>
      <ul style="margin:6px 0 6px 20px; color:#999;">
        <li><strong>Account data:</strong> username, email (optional), password (hashed)</li>
        <li><strong>Content:</strong> posts, threads, private messages, uploaded files, reports</li>
        <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser user agent, access timestamps</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> session cookies required for authentication</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">2. How We Use Your Information</h3>
      <p>We use your information to:</p>
      <ul style="margin:6px 0 6px 20px; color:#999;">
        <li>Provide and operate the Forum</li>
        <li>Authenticate your account and maintain sessions</li>
        <li>Display your posts and profile to other users</li>
        <li>Enforce our Terms of Service and Forum Rules</li>
        <li>Protect against abuse, spam, and malicious activity</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">3. Data Storage</h3>
      <p>Your data is stored on secure servers. Passwords are hashed using bcrypt and are never stored in plain text. Uploaded files are stored on Cloudflare R2 cloud storage.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">4. Data Sharing</h3>
      <p>We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may disclose information if required by law or to protect the rights and safety of our users.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">5. Cookies</h3>
      <p>We use essential session cookies for authentication. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics. Your session cookie expires after 24 hours of inactivity.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">6. Your Rights</h3>
      <p>You have the right to:</p>
      <ul style="margin:6px 0 6px 20px; color:#999;">
        <li>Access your personal data through your profile page</li>
        <li>Update or correct your information at any time</li>
        <li>Request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">7. Data Retention</h3>
      <p>We retain your data for as long as your account is active. If you request account deletion, we will remove your personal data within 30 days. Some content (posts, threads) may be anonymized rather than deleted to preserve discussion context.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">8. Security</h3>
      <p>We implement security measures including HTTPS/TLS encryption, secure session cookies, rate limiting, and regular security updates. However, no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">9. Children's Privacy</h3>
      <p>The Forum is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If we learn that we have collected such data, we will delete it promptly.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">10. Changes to This Policy</h3>
      <p>We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify users of significant changes via a forum announcement.</p>

      <h3 style="color:#cfcfcf; font-size:13px; margin:16px 0 6px;">11. Contact</h3>
      <p>For privacy-related inquiries, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@unknownforums.fun">admin@unknownforums.fun</a>.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
